```plantuml
@startuml dylanvanh_MunchOut

actor Customer
actor Restaurant
boundary FlutterFrontend
control AuthBloc
control LoginBloc
control SignupBloc
control RestaurantBloc
control CustomerBloc
database FlaskBackend

== User Authentication ==
Customer -> FlutterFrontend: Open App
FlutterFrontend -> AuthBloc: Check Authentication Status
AuthBloc -> FlaskBackend: Verify Session
FlaskBackend -> AuthBloc: Return Session Status
AuthBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Update UI

Customer -> FlutterFrontend: Login Request
FlutterFrontend -> LoginBloc: Process Login
LoginBloc -> FlaskBackend: Authenticate User
FlaskBackend -> LoginBloc: Return Auth Token
LoginBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Update UI with Auth Status

Restaurant -> FlutterFrontend: Signup Request
FlutterFrontend -> SignupBloc: Process Signup
SignupBloc -> FlaskBackend: Register Restaurant
FlaskBackend -> SignupBloc: Return Registration Status
SignupBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Update UI with Signup Result

== Event Management (Restaurant) ==
Restaurant -> FlutterFrontend: Create Event
FlutterFrontend -> RestaurantBloc: Handle Event Creation
RestaurantBloc -> FlaskBackend: Submit Event Data
FlaskBackend -> RestaurantBloc: Return Event Confirmation
RestaurantBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Update UI with Event Status

Restaurant -> FlutterFrontend: View Events
FlutterFrontend -> RestaurantBloc: Fetch Event List
RestaurantBloc -> FlaskBackend: Request Event Data
FlaskBackend -> RestaurantBloc: Return Event Data
RestaurantBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Display Event List

== Booking Management (Customer) ==
Customer -> FlutterFrontend: Browse Events
FlutterFrontend -> CustomerBloc: Fetch Available Events
CustomerBloc -> FlaskBackend: Request Event Listings
FlaskBackend -> CustomerBloc: Return Event Listings
CustomerBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Display Events

Customer -> FlutterFrontend: Book Event
FlutterFrontend -> CustomerBloc: Handle Booking
CustomerBloc -> FlaskBackend: Submit Booking Request
FlaskBackend -> CustomerBloc: Return Booking Confirmation
CustomerBloc -> FlutterFrontend: Update UI with Booking Status

@enduml
```